latestPosts.caption:
“Alomei Cosmetics Expands! ✨ Now Open at Central Plaza, 5th Floor, Kohima, Nagaland. Visit us for premium beauty products and an elevated shopping experience!”
Video by @sanjeevtamangofficial 

Alomei Cosmetics, founded by Mrs. Themsao Khiamniungan Odyuo, is a brand dedicated to addressing skin issues through natural and herbal extracts. The company offers additional healthcare services, including skin, hair, and homeo-aesthetic clinics. The founder emphasizes a commitment to quality products and a holistic approach to health via homeopathy, aiming to enhance natural beauty and promote overall well-being. ￼

In recognition of her contributions, Mrs Themsao Khiamniungan Odyuo  was honored at the Global Women Inspiration Award and Conclave 2024. ￼
